OutputStream = new ObjectOutputStream(serialized)) {\n            objectOutputStream.writeObject(publicKey);\n        }\n        return serialized.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static PublicKey deserialize(byte[] serialized) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream objectInputStream = new ObjectInputStream(\n                new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized))) {\n            return (PublicKey)objectInputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 4214, "output": 1097, "cacheRead": 12800, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 18111, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780878598123, "responseId": "resp_0fad95056ccf6a41016a260d0678bc8195a586a54fb8034adc"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_LyynJUywUo7A6dCuyLRjn70X|fc_0fad95056ccf6a41016a260d0e2c6881959340887c382f7a63", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2784 bytes to tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk18on/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk18on/BCBIKEPublicKeyTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780878612642}]}
